CONCLUSION
━━━━━━━━━━

You now have 50+ battle-tested prompts. Here is my recommendation
for getting started:

Week 1: Master Prompts 1-10 (Email Writing)
Week 2: Master Prompts 11-20 (Content Creation)
Week 3: Master Prompts 21-28 (Business Analysis)
Week 4: Master Prompts 29-35 (Coding Assistance)
Week 5+: Explore the rest and create your own variations

Remember: The goal is not to have the perfect prompt. It is to get
stuff done. Start with what resonates, iterate as you go.

